snippet.title: Sleeping Dogs Available Now
snippet.description:
Sleeping Dogs is now available in North America! 
Loyalty. Honor. Sacrifice. Those are the qualities Wei Shen needs to chop the head off the Sun On Yee dragon. But he'll also need to display ruthlessness, cold blood and brutal fighting skills. So does that make him a good man gone bad, or was there always a seed of evil inside him? 
That's up to you! How far will you go to take down the Triad? 

Song : The Heavy -- What Makes A Good Man

For more information about the game, visit:
Official site: http://www.sleepingdogs.net
Forum: http://forums.sleepingdogs.net/
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/sleepingdogsgame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/#!/sleepingdogs
Tumblr: http://sleepingdogs.tumblr.com/
